{
  "title": "Rooted™ Executive Reset Survey",
  "introduction": "First of all, thank you for your time and willingness to complete this questionnaire. In the busyness of everyday life, we often forget to pause and reflect on how we care for ourselves — physically, mentally, and emotionally.\n\nThis questionnaire is designed not only to help you reflect on your habits and challenges around nutrition, energy, and overall well-being, but also to gather valuable insights to better support leaders like you.\n\nWe aim to gain an understanding of your lifestyle habits, the obstacles you face in achieving the life you want, and how we can support leaders in making sustainable changes.\n\nPlease take a moment to answer the questions thoroughly and honestly. The more detailed and open your responses, the better we can understand what helps you perform at your best — both at work and in your personal life.\n\nThere are no wrong answers. This is about your personal experiences, habits, and challenges. The survey is completely anonymous, and all data will be treated confidentially. Your input will only be used for shaping the academy program and will be deleted afterward.\n\nThank you again for your openness and valuable time. Let’s explore where you currently stand and how you can live and work with more balance and energy.",
